snippet.title: Space Channel 5 VR Official English Trailer - "Space Channel 5 VR Kinda Funky News Flash!” PV ver.1
snippet.description:
Space Channel 5 is SEGA’s legendary Dreamcast rhythm game first released 20 years ago and now coming to Virtual Reality! Come and experience the return of Ulala for yourselves. Stay tuned everyone!!

Game Title      : Space Channel 5 VR Kinda Funky News Flash!
Developed by  : Grounding Inc. http://www.g-rounding.com/en/
Game               : http://www.sc5-vr.com/
Hardware        : HTC VIVE™, PlayStation® VR
Language        : Japanese, English
Trailer by         : Kert Gartner http://kertgartner.com
Copyright        : ©SEGA ©Grounding Inc.
*“Space Channel 5” is a registered trademark of SEGA Holdings Co., Ltd. 

＜Other Language＞
Japanese                  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ahyLFrJr6ao
Chinese (繁体字)　 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-bxeLMV3gPc

Are you a VR arcade owner and you have a business offer? 
Please contact at press@g-rounding.com

THANK YOU FOR WATCHING!
